seo: 三星, WLAN AP, WEA453e, 远程命令执行, 漏洞
seo_en: Samsung, WLAN AP, WEA453e, Remote Command Execution, Vulnerability
summary: 该插件用于检测三星 WLAN AP WEA453e 设备是否存在远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求来验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect if the Samsung WLAN AP WEA453e device has a remote command execution vulnerability by sending specific requests to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
